{"tid":710050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無恥收機佬即場壓價 藉口多多 小心此人","createTime":"2018-06-20T12:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T13:04:07.000Z","uid":27640,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ee69362dd89dfbce17c21e48e13cfbb2cfd208","tid":710050,"uid":27640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:41:07.000Z","msg":"借人ac開po<br />\n話說 我本身都有用開一個app放二手野<br />\n咁我就係個app到賣一部爆咗Lcd既6s<br />\n之後個收機佬就出價約左我出去交收 仲留咗電話俾我 <br />\n當我見到個電話號碼 原來我之前都放過一部機俾佢  咁我就諗應該無死啦 之次同佢交收過都無事<br />\n<br />\n當我地見到面佢就黎料喇 <br />\n因為我部機跌壞左Lcd 有半邊mon touch唔到 所以check機都比較困難 <br />\n佢就係到話我部機有sim lock 要用卡貼 佢唔收<br />\n我心諗 邊有可能 我一直都用香港sim卡<br />\n之後我話無可能嫁喎 你再check下先?<br />\n之後佢就話我部機咁樣check唔到 就放自己張sim card落去 見到上到網就無出聲<br />\n過咗陣佢又話<br />\n佢：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你部樣咁樣我唔收嫁喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：吓 點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你個mon爆埋入面我唔收嫁 唔知cpu個啲有無事 你張相都無個啲黑邊(姐係爆Lcd個啲一條條黑色野)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：吓 我張相有影埋嫁喎 同埋我description box有話爆Lcd嫁喎 你依家話唔要就唔要 要人地特燈出黎同你交收？<br />\n之後佢靜咗一陣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咁你依家係咪唔要部機先？總之淨係做到$500<br />\n之後我就走左<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/203520_ed15020a49ce76933c6a4cf118c145ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F203520_ed15020a49ce76933c6a4cf118c145ab.png&h=8c76f6cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有圖有真相<br />\n我po上黎只係想大家係交收前 買賣家雙方都清楚了解咗產品既情況先 唔好好似我咁 浪費時間 車錢<br />\n同埋有部分收機佬真係好狗 即場壓價等等 <br />\n佢電話 51666234 大家買賣電話前記得睇睇係唔係喱個號碼 係既話..自己諗吓好唔好係佢到買/賣機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5c7ec5c75afc372176e4631962ab038735c6ec","tid":710050,"uid":27640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:42:25.000Z","msg":"推 等多啲人知道 小心喱個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3f3534d0dafdd79f8c037325b2a8b284ace2ba","tid":710050,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:42:49.000Z","msg":"唔壓你價點賺錢"},{"pid":"112db33e7455d22784cc03d019ec29a4ef804d6b","tid":710050,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:43:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36239fb48e6f7f03f237e14ab6f8676cd53e3b02","tid":710050,"uid":652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:43:55.000Z","msg":"番大陸整完再賣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561e48a4d237270d7202da8f82a0223425d3ca3f","tid":710050,"uid":149902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:44:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13b5946f3f74a12d29240d464f19f382588781d2","tid":710050,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:44:14.000Z","msg":"800我收"},{"pid":"584ed6b65a5ece65dde27720166e34a4fa653415","tid":710050,"uid":27640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36239fb48e6f7f03f237e14ab6f8676cd53e3b02","tid":710050,"uid":652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:43:55.000Z","msg":"番大陸整完再賣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:47:00.000Z","msg":"就係懶得去整先賣 唉"},{"pid":"698c04453c29f2f02c080d3b190856945782098a","tid":710050,"uid":27640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13b5946f3f74a12d29240d464f19f382588781d2","tid":710050,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T1